<p>'All of them have been out of our price range so we ended up buying a projector from the post office. Then we went to Spotlight and bought a blockout roller blind to use as the screen.'</p>

<p>She showed a picture of her contraption, which is approximately two metres wide, and can easily be moved outside for 'BBQ movies'.   </p>

<p>The projector weighs just 4.5 kilos and can project as wide as five metres onto a flat surface.</p>

